&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;#2018-10-29 12:36:10.407911&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;#diff = 2.201889 s&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-comment&quot;&gt;#when using int only&lt;/span&gt;
